    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Those who vote in a group's elections and on other occasions of decision making, usually citizens of a community or otherwise members of the group. For the general term referring to people qualified and registered to vote, prefer "electors (general, people by activity)," although usage overlaps.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
